<section_header_level_1><loc_108><loc_88><loc_345><loc_97>d. Combination of Flexible Work Arrangements</section_header_level_1>
<unordered_list><list_item><loc_128><loc_103><loc_454><loc_136>i Offices may adopt a combination of Skeleton Workforce and WFH arrangement as their regular work set-up for DepEd Personnel; as may be applicable: This arrangement shall be limited to one (1) WFH and four (4) at Skeleton Workforce or on-site reporting: day days</list_item>
<list_item><loc_128><loc_141><loc_455><loc_182>DepEd officials and employees under this arrangement may choose the of their preferred WFH arrangement between Tuesday to Friday only, subject to the approval of the Heads of Functional Office. Heads of Functional Office shall ensure the equal distribution of employees present on-site per day day.</list_item>
</unordered_list>
